response.overview: She’s finally back!! It's the lovely Shihono Ryo-chan. While maintaining her signature slender physique, her soft curves have become even more prominent! She draws you in wearing a series of outfits that push the absolute limit. Whether she's amidst a refreshing grove of trees or standing in a river flowing through the forest—you will undoubtedly find yourself catching your breath! This is a powerful, full-effort work packed with a side of Ryo-chan's charm that you've never seen before!
response.title: しほの涼 Aphrodite
